---
title: Open-Faced Pork Sausage Sandwiches on Cheesy Garlic Bread with Green Bell Peppers & Onion
description: There are few combinations more satisfying than sausage and peppers. After all, with the sweet caramelization on the peps and the super-savory notes in the meat, what could be more comforting? Here, the dynamic duo star in an effortless dinner that comes together on just two baking sheets. While the herb-seasoned bell peppers, onion, and sausage roast, cheesy garlic bread toasts alongside. Add a creamy garlic sauce for dipping or drizzling, and you’ve got effortlessly cozy cuisine at its finest.
